  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed additional storey on top of the existing rear extension, together with the continuation of the pitched roof-line of the existing two-storey rear projection would result in an overall bulk of projection which would be out of proportion to the host building & out of character with the terrace of which the property forms a part. It would also represent an over-development on this modestly-sized site. The proposal would conflict with Policies D1, D4 & D11 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 & with the design principles for extensions set out in the supplementary Islington Urban Design Guide 2006"
